This is DCF77 encode program on ATTiny13. Input date and time from
serial. Original code development on AVR Studio by ATTiny11.
I convert avr-as and ATTiny13. And add some enhancement.

Input date and time

YY-MM-DD/W HH:MM<CR>

W is monday is 1 and sunday is 7

Original page

http://elektronik-kompendium.de/public/arnerossius/schaltungen/avr/dcfsim.htm

Replacing ATtiny11/12 by ATtiny13

http://www.atmel.com/Images/doc4297.pdf


Test on Arduino DCF77 library by set VERBOSE_DEBUG.


rCT

